title: Vizio 24" D24 D1 smart TV Review! 2016
description:
2016 Best Budget Friendly Television Vizio D24 D1 24 inch under $200 Purchase this TV off Amazon: http://amzn.to/2iX02GT (Affiliate)

Anytime you're looking to buy a TV make sure it has a 3.5MM HEADPHONE JACK (THIS IS SO IMPORTANT)
Also make sure it's at least 1080P
720p is a little low if you plan on using it for your console.

The Vizio D24-D1 24 inch is a 1080p Smart tv with integrated apps like Netflix, Netflix, amazon instant video, iHeartRadio, VUDU, HuluPlus, YouTube, Pandora at just a click of the button.
